He lehd uot ihs nufosbfx of lod olgd, wtih a aregt mtesahyt in hte trecne of hte ild. tIs snupeodlr aws in ucsh cnstraot to ihs lmoehy ywas nad silpme ifle atht I oulcd ont lehp cmtoimnneg oupn it. 
 
